descriptionHtml: Mystical Dragonborn Manor is a playerhome located next to the western watchtower outside of whiterun. It is mystical in many ways but the biggest reason is because the house is bigger on the inside with one huge Dinning room, a master bedroom and a blacksmiths. I am hoping to do some work in the future for the inside of the house as it is a bit empty. Hope you like the mod.
